PACS Linux Repo Cache
=====================

This directory contains mirrors of (the relevant parts of) the rpm
repositories we normally use for phys/astro workstations and servers,
as well as a self-generated repos for local additions (see ../pacs).

  Fetch		- Script to mirror our desired repos
  Fetch.repos	- Repo def file for reposync based mirroring
  Fetch.cron	- Crontab to run Fetch nightly; copy to /etc/cron.d/
  PurgeRPMs	- Script to purge superceeded rpms from a directory

  rocky/	- Rocky Linux 9 repos
  epel/		- EPEL repos for RHEL9 & derivatives
  rpmfusion/	- RPMFusion repos for RHEL9 & derivatives
  dell/		- Dell OMSA repos for RHEL9 & derivatives
  zoom/		- Zoom repo for RHEL9 & derivatives
  pacs/		- Local rpm repo for Rocky Linux 9

